reviews.review_text: 4-29-89 Irvine This was a great show to be at. One of my favs to pull out and listen to also, especially the second set. The China/Rider is very nice and the Looks Like Rain is oh so sweet! Of note after the drums/space interlude..  a great Other One and a very tasty Wharf Rat. Also, the He's Gone is the Abby Hoffman memorial version.

4/29/1989 Well played, pretty mellow energy-wise, good sound.

Highlight: O1>Wharf Rat
Blow Away Love Blow Away (among others) here! Thank you!
